;+
; NAME:
;       BOX::CLEANUP
;
; PURPOSE:
;
;       This is the BOX object class destructor method.
;
; SYNTAX:
;
;       Called automatically when the object is destroyed.
;
; ARGUMENTS:
;
;       None.
;
; KEYWORDS:
;
;      None.
;-
